        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>  <!-- Halaman Kontak -->  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-6">Hubungi Kami</h1>
      <p class="mb-4">Punya pertanyaan, saran, atau ingin kerja sama? Kami senang mendengarnya!</p><form action="#" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
    <div>
      <label for="nama" class="block mb-1 font-medium">Nama</label>
      <input type="text" id="nama" name="nama" required class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded px-3 py-2">
    </div>
    <div>
      <label for="email" class="block mb-1 font-medium">Email</label>
